    "description": "Every 6 seconds, there is a 23% chance to trigger a 6-second buff. The effect remains active after weapon swaps.\n\nBuff effects: +1 projectile, +20% damage, +50% fire rate, +100% reload speed, 50% chance to fire an extra shot, and shots ricochet once on impact then split into two."
